scene.message:
Nanjo: Will the day come when{nl}
our town's convenience stores{nl}
sell weapons too, I wonder?{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Tch, all weapons, huh.{nl}
Without a book section, it{nl}
feels kinda lonely.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Look at this drawing —{nl}
real stylish, huh!{wait_fr:32}{nl}
...Huh, it's the real thing?{waitkey}{ret}

Clerk: Hi~ everyone, how's it{nl}
going? Welcome to Yin & Yan!{nl}
Now, what'll you buy for me~?{waitkey}{ret}

Clerk: Oh no~ Don't tell me{nl}
you're a robber~?{waitkey}{clearbox}I don't like naughty kids{nl}
like that!{waitkey}{ret}

Customer: Have you met the{nl}
Harem Queen yet?{waitkey}{clearbox}The Queen is a terribly{nl}
delicate person, you know!{waitkey}{clearbox}Listen, whatever you do, be{nl}
sure not to hurt the Queen!{waitkey}{ret}

Customer: They say the Queen{nl}
is gone now! Finally we can{nl}
breathe easy!{waitkey}{ret}
